---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  lang="sk"
  title="TFWS verify | nakupovanie.sk / nakupovani.cz"
  description="Verification page for TFWS 2.0 artifacts"
  canonical="/verify.html"
>
  <main class="page-shell">
    <div class="container stack">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-inner">
          <div class="kicker">TFWS 2.0</div>
          <h1 class="h2">Verify artifacts</h1>
          <p class="lead">
            This page exposes the human-readable trust layer for the domain sale project.
            It is intentionally static, hashable, and compatible with the TFWS publishing model.
          </p>
          <p class="muted">
            The live site publishes a domain-first trust manifest, a signed inventory path, a
            human entrypoint, and machine entrypoints under <code>/.well-known/</code>.
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-2" style="margin-top:18px;">
            <div class="notice">
              <strong>Human entrypoint</strong><br />
              <span class="small">/sk • /cz • /en</span>
            </div>
            <div class="notice">
              <strong>Machine entrypoints</strong><br />
              <span class="small">/.well-known/ai-trust-hub.json • /.well-known/llms.txt • /.well-known/search-discovery.json</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="card">
        <div class="card-inner">
          <h2 style="margin-top:0;">Verification checklist</h2>
          <ol class="muted" style="padding-left: 20px; margin: 12px 0 0;">
            <li>Open the human landing page in the required language.</li>
            <li>Inspect the trust manifest at <code>/.well-known/ai-trust-hub.json</code>.</li>
            <li>Verify the hash inventory at <code>/dumps/sha256.json</code>.</li>
            <li>Check the declared public key and key history.</li>
            <li>Confirm the admin and policy links resolve cleanly.</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="card">
        <div class="card-inner">
          <h2 style="margin-top:0;">Publishing model</h2>
          <p class="muted">
            nakupovanie.sk / nakupovani.cz is published as a static, audit-friendly showcase with
            a trust manifest, hash inventory, and signed-artifact-ready structure.
          </p>
          <p class="muted">
            The current bundle includes the TFWS 2.0 scaffold. Final signature material can be added
            later during deployment with your chosen signing key flow.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="card">
        <div class="card-inner">
          <h2 style="margin-top:0;">Linked resources</h2>
          <div class="footer-links">
            <a href="/ai-trust-hub.html">trust hub</a>
            <a href="/.well-known/ai-trust-hub.json">ai-trust-hub.json</a>
            <a href="/.well-known/llms.txt">llms.txt</a>
            <a href="/.well-known/search-discovery.json">search-discovery.json</a>
            <a href="/control/panel/">admin</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
